{
  "dashboard": {
    "title": "GL-007 FurnacePerformanceMonitor - Executive KPIs",
    "tags": ["gl-007", "executive", "kpis", "business"],
    "timezone": "utc",
    "editable": true,
    "graphTooltip": 1,
    "time": {
      "from": "now-30d",
      "to": "now"
    },
    "refresh": "5m",
    "panels": [
      {
        "title": "Fleet-Wide Avg Thermal Efficiency",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 0},
        "type": "gauge",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "avg(gl_007_furnace_thermal_efficiency_percent)",
            "legendFormat": "Efficiency %"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "showThresholdLabels": true,
          "showThresholdMarkers": true
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "red"},
                {"value": 70, "color": "orange"},
                {"value": 80, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 85, "color": "green"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "Annual Energy Savings (Projected)",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 0},
        "type": "stat",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(gl_007_annual_energy_savings_usd)",
            "legendFormat": "Savings"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "colorMode": "value",
          "graphMode": "area",
          "textMode": "value_and_name"
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "currencyUSD",
            "decimals": 0,
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "red"},
                {"value": 100000, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 250000, "color": "green"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "Annual Carbon Reduction (Projected)",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 0},
        "type": "stat",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(gl_007_annual_carbon_reduction_tons)",
            "legendFormat": "CO2 Reduction"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "colorMode": "value",
          "graphMode": "area",
          "textMode": "value_and_name"
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "tons",
            "decimals": 0,
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "red"},
                {"value": 500, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 1000, "color": "green"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "Fleet Availability (30d)",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 0},
        "type": "gauge",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "avg(avg_over_time(gl_007_production_uptime_percent[30d]))",
            "legendFormat": "Uptime %"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "showThresholdLabels": true,
          "showThresholdMarkers": true
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "red"},
                {"value": 90, "color": "orange"},
                {"value": 95, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 98, "color": "green"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "Energy Savings Trend ($/hr)",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 6},
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(gl_007_energy_cost_savings_usd_hr) by (furnace_id)",
            "legendFormat": "{{furnace_id}}"
          },
          {
            "expr": "sum(gl_007_energy_cost_savings_usd_hr)",
            "legendFormat": "Total Fleet"
          }
        ],
        "yaxes": [
          {"format": "currencyUSD", "label": "Savings $/hr"},
          {"format": "short"}
        ],
        "stack": false
      },
      {
        "title": "Carbon Emissions Reduction (kg/hr)",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 6},
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(gl_007_carbon_emissions_reduction_kg_hr) by (furnace_id)",
            "legendFormat": "{{furnace_id}}"
          },
          {
            "expr": "sum(gl_007_carbon_emissions_reduction_kg_hr)",
            "legendFormat": "Total Fleet"
          }
        ],
        "yaxes": [
          {"format": "kg/h", "label": "CO2 Reduction"},
          {"format": "short"}
        ],
        "stack": false
      },
      {
        "title": "Fleet Performance Score Card",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 14},
        "type": "table",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "avg(gl_007_furnace_thermal_efficiency_percent) by (furnace_id)",
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true,
            "legendFormat": "Efficiency"
          },
          {
            "expr": "avg(gl_007_furnace_specific_energy_consumption_kwh_ton) by (furnace_id)",
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true,
            "legendFormat": "SEC"
          },
          {
            "expr": "avg(gl_007_production_uptime_percent) by (furnace_id)",
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true,
            "legendFormat": "Uptime"
          },
          {
            "expr": "avg(gl_007_energy_cost_savings_usd_hr) by (furnace_id)",
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true,
            "legendFormat": "Savings"
          }
        ],
        "transformations": [
          {
            "id": "merge",
            "options": {}
          },
          {
            "id": "organize",
            "options": {
              "excludeByName": {"Time": true, "job": true, "__name__": true},
              "renameByName": {
                "furnace_id": "Furnace",
                "Value #A": "Efficiency %",
                "Value #B": "SEC (kWh/ton)",
                "Value #C": "Uptime %",
                "Value #D": "Savings ($/hr)"
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "title": "Efficiency Distribution by Furnace",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 22},
        "type": "bargauge",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "avg(gl_007_furnace_thermal_efficiency_percent) by (furnace_id)",
            "legendFormat": "{{furnace_id}}"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "displayMode": "gradient",
          "orientation": "horizontal",
          "showUnfilled": true
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "red"},
                {"value": 70, "color": "orange"},
                {"value": 80, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 85, "color": "green"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "Fuel Consumption by Type",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 22},
        "type": "piechart",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(gl_007_furnace_fuel_consumption_kg_hr) by (fuel_type)",
            "legendFormat": "{{fuel_type}}"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "legend": {
            "displayMode": "table",
            "placement": "right",
            "values": ["value", "percent"]
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "Maintenance Alerts by Severity (30d)",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 30},
        "type": "piechart",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(increase(gl_007_maintenance_alerts_total[30d])) by (severity)",
            "legendFormat": "{{severity}}"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "legend": {
            "displayMode": "table",
            "placement": "bottom",
            "values": ["value"]
          }
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "overrides": [
            {
              "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "critical"},
              "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed"}}]
            },
            {
              "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "warning"},
              "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"fixedColor": "yellow", "mode": "fixed"}}]
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "Total Maintenance Cost Avoidance (30d)",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 30},
        "type": "stat",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(increase(gl_007_maintenance_cost_avoidance_usd_total[30d]))",
            "legendFormat": "Cost Avoided"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "colorMode": "value",
          "graphMode": "area"
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "currencyUSD",
            "decimals": 0
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "ML Model Prediction Accuracy",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 30},
        "type": "gauge",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "avg(gl_007_prediction_accuracy) by (model_type)",
            "legendFormat": "{{model_type}}"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "showThresholdLabels": false,
          "showThresholdMarkers": true
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percentunit",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 1,
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "red"},
                {"value": 0.85, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 0.90, "color": "green"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "ROI Analysis - Energy Savings vs Investment",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 36},
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(gl_007_annual_energy_savings_usd) by (furnace_id)",
            "legendFormat": "Annual Savings - {{furnace_id}}"
          }
        ],
        "yaxes": [
          {"format": "currencyUSD", "label": "Annual Savings"},
          {"format": "short"}
        ],
        "seriesOverrides": [
          {
            "alias": "/Annual Savings.*/",
            "bars": true,
            "lines": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "title": "Cumulative CO2 Reduction (30d)",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 36},
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(increase(gl_007_carbon_emissions_reduction_kg_hr[1h])) / 1000",
            "legendFormat": "Cumulative CO2 (tons)"
          }
        ],
        "yaxes": [
          {"format": "tons", "label": "CO2 Reduction"},
          {"format": "short"}
        ],
        "fill": 2
      },
      {
        "title": "Compliance & Quality Metrics",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 44},
        "type": "stat",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "avg(gl_007_determinism_score_percent)",
            "legendFormat": "Determinism Score"
          },
          {
            "expr": "100 * (1 - sum(rate(gl_007_http_requests_total{status=\"error\"}[30d])) / sum(rate(gl_007_http_requests_total[30d])))",
            "legendFormat": "Success Rate"
          },
          {
            "expr": "100 * avg_over_time(up{job=\"gl-007-furnace-monitor\"}[30d])",
            "legendFormat": "Availability"
          },
          {
            "expr": "avg(gl_007_scada_connection_status) * 100",
            "legendFormat": "SCADA Connectivity"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "colorMode": "background",
          "graphMode": "area",
          "textMode": "value_and_name"
        },
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "red"},
                {"value": 95, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 99, "color": "green"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "title": "Key Performance Indicators Summary",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 50},
        "type": "text",
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "# GL-007 FurnacePerformanceMonitor - Executive Summary\n\n## Business Impact\n- **Energy Efficiency**: Continuous monitoring and optimization of thermal efficiency across furnace fleet\n- **Cost Savings**: Real-time identification of efficiency losses and optimization opportunities\n- **Carbon Reduction**: Quantified CO2 emissions reduction through improved operations\n- **Predictive Maintenance**: ML-powered maintenance forecasting reduces unplanned downtime\n\n## Technical Excellence\n- **Zero-Hallucination Guarantee**: 100% deterministic calculations with full provenance tracking\n- **High Availability**: 99.9% uptime SLA with automated failover\n- **SCADA Integration**: Real-time data from industrial control systems\n- **Advanced Analytics**: ML models for efficiency prediction and anomaly detection\n\n## Compliance & Quality\n- **Determinism Verification**: All calculations reproducible and auditable\n- **Data Quality**: Continuous monitoring of sensor health and data integrity\n- **Regulatory Compliance**: Automated tracking of operational parameters\n- **Performance Transparency**: Complete visibility into agent operations"
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
